message.content:
I'll put together a healthy meal plan for you for today!
Breakfast: A bowl of oatmeal topped with blueberries, walnuts, and honey.
Lunch: A veggie-packed salad with quinoa, avocado, grilled chicken, and lemon vinaigrette dressing.
Dinner: Baked fish with roasted potatoes and sautéed green beans.
Snack: An apple with almond butter or a smoothie made with bananas, spinach, Greek yogurt, and honey.
